{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回 血溅洞房\n\n本章主要讲述楚留香与胡铁花在洞房中的对话。胡铁花新婚之夜发现新娘子并非琵琶公主，而是另有其人。两人在洞房中发现了一具女尸，血溅洞房，引发了一系列谜团。胡铁花对新娘子的身份和美貌感到惊讶，而楚留香则对新娘子的身份产生怀疑。本章通过对话展现了胡铁花的性格特点，以及楚留香的机智和观察力。\n\n主要人物：楚留香、胡铁花、琵琶公主、龟兹王、新娘子\n主要地点：洞房、帐篷\n主要事件：发现女尸、讨论新娘子身份",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你还好么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你可瞧见了你的新娘子?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的以为我是个呆女婿?连新媳妇都不看就跑出洞房来?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你……你……不生气?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为何要生气?我简直从来就没有这样开心过。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的酒醒了么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也从来没有这样清醒过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自然已知道我那媳妇并不是琵琶公主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你想，我那新媳妇既不敢露面，必定是个大麻子、丑八怪，否则又怎会不敢见人……是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许并不太丑，只不过……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道不相信?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……也许是……也许是……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好!你不相信，我就带你去见她。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一大清早，你就要拉着我去闯洞房，这像话么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自己兄弟，这又有什么关系?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算你认为没关系，但新娘子呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你反正是要见他的，何必……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你几时离开这里的?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我刚刚出去找你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这片刻之间，就有人进来下了毒手!这人会是谁?他和你有何仇恨?为何要在你新婚之夕杀死你的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你以为这就是我的新媳妇?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道不是?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然不是，这女人是谁，我一辈子都没有见过她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……那么新娘子在哪里?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这究竟是怎么回事?这女人怎会赤裸裸地跑到我床上来?她是什么时候来的?我媳妇难道不知道?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这女人并非是自己跑来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎知道?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就更奇怪了，别人杀死她后，为何要移到这里来?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你出去的时懊，新娘子真的还睡在这床上?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，她明明还睡得很熟，现在……现在怎地不见了?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来人呀!我屋子里死了人，你们快来看看这人是谁?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这女人是谁?你们……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为何要杀她?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我杀了她?你见了鬼么?我和她素不相识，为何要杀她?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她纵然生得丑些，但好歹也是你的妻子，你怎能下得了这样的毒手?你……你简直不是人，是畜生!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说什么?这女人是……是我的妻子?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她就算生得丑些，但究竟也是金枝玉叶，哪点配不上你这流氓?你……你就算不愿娶她，也不该……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人疯了，这人疯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你才疯了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "床上的这位姑娘究竟是谁?王爷认得么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的女儿，我怎会不认得?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昨夜你给胡铁花的新娘子，就是这位姑娘?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然就是她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我将我自己的女儿嫁给你，我自己难道还不知道?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若说这丑八怪就是新娘子，我昨夜见着的又是谁呢?难道还有人会来冒充新娘子不成?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你杀了她，还要来说这些鬼话骗人?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为何要骗你?我昨夜难道遇见了鬼不成?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "他实在也不知",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "新娘子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算你昨夜见到的不是我姐姐，我姐姐又怎会死在你床上?不是你杀了她，是谁杀了她?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一定是你们故意将新娘子掉了包，却来冤枉我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁!我难道会杀死我亲生的女儿不成?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你为何不帮我说句话，你难道也不相信我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要我说什么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你杀了人就得偿命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你想走?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我走又怎样?难道还有谁拦得住我?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你走不了的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎会跟你动手?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，咱们就一齐走吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "更走不得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若一走，冤枉就更洗不清了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别的事无妨，这件事却非弄清楚不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就知道你舍不得走的，好，你不走我走。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的不让我走?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要去哪里?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里不可去?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大漠非比中原，你一个人只怕哪里都去不得。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既不肯陪我走，我死了也用不着你费心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你到底要我怎样?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你为什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他若走了呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他若走了，我替你女儿偿命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三天之内，你若找不出真凶来呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我相信你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人明明可以走的，却偏偏不走，反而立下这样的誓，他们究竟是为什么呢?我姐姐难道真不是他杀的?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是他杀的是谁杀的?天下难道真的会有愿意冒充别人老婆的女人?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说老实话，我也并非真的想走，这件事不弄清楚，我也不甘心，死的这人若真是龟兹王的女儿，我昨夜见到的那人又是谁呢?她为什么要来冒充新娘子?这对她又有什么好处?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还想不通么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想不通。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为何我要相信?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为她生得太丑，所以龟兹王才一直瞒着你，否则琵琶公主既敢出来乱跑，她为何躲着不敢见人?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四五个时辰?难道我还未进洞房时，她已被别人杀了?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但她的尸身……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说……你说昨天晚上我们在床上时，床底下有个死尸?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她……她明知床底下有死尸，还能和我……和我在床上……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    }
